This spacious home features an open concept floor plan, study with custom built-ins, versatile living area with fireplace, inviting kitchen with breakfast bar, center island and dining area, spacious primary suite with sitting room and multiple walk in closets. The outdoor space is complete with expansive wraparound porches, gated entrance, circular drive, oversized detached garage, agriculture barn and is completely fenced with mature trees.
